               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmmǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 41ra-179ra)&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 41ra-8rb)&#xD; I-2) Taʾāmmǝra
                     Māryām “Miracles of Mary”: 153 miracles (fols. 9ra-176vb)&#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd
                     laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee…” (fols. 177ra-177vb)&#xD; I-4)
                     Introductory exhortation (fols. 69rb-70vb, 177vb-179ra)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
